{"tid":2492814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用指甲自殘會留疤嗎","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:49:18.000Z","uid":395436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ea305444a836ee7043b5d721bb0079a26b2e0714","tid":2492814,"uid":395436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"大家好，小妹台灣人，不太會說廣東話還請見諒<br />\n因為怕在台灣網站被認出來所以來這裡發問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概半個月過去了一直都還有疤痕<br />\n想請問即使是用指甲割的一樣會留疤嗎⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n沒有血腥，<br />\n但還是怕有人會介意所以放一下防雷圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmaz5aBawLv6HUygZ9XJFMHvh1kwZA9YvMAaNspPMYrWK6?filename=eBZBQ0Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBZBQ0Y.png&h=976aae68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在台北一間餐廳的西多士<br />\n真係好好食呀😭😭 真心好鍾意港式飲茶<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n今年 3/30 的半夜用指甲先狂劃，劃到紅腫之後又用沒有筆芯的自動筆筆頭狂劃，但其實只有紅腫跟一點點破皮，根本沒流血<br />\n<br />\n然後3/30 約下午五點看是這樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPosTw2VUtAWyYV9G4pRkr4rxt7y2efJH6AS85QD64oKr?filename=tCEqKpN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCEqKpN.png&h=e625df73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近看大概是這樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPnj7UHX1ZoaSR2df6LadSJVfKoGRWG6HdRXdUQXuSMh7?filename=06JSpp2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06JSpp2.png&h=de633c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔天3/31 一早變得非常紅非常明顯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSKtJEPpWTjvQeZyJL9KACotvijmpaKmeEomGwk9ApC7a?filename=xx7vVwY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxx7vVwY.png&h=0d654999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間就沒有特別紀錄了，<br />\n但到現在都還有疤痕（剛剛拍的）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNZ4TWQeb9iNHngRwVEaZYVPDzWC6L8yAKWXiYhD4GEGb?filename=pFMsXLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFMsXLq.jpg&h=992a6ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請問這個到底會不會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後㊗️大家都幸福平安快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}